                <text type="uv_alert">Sun protection 10:00am to 2:30pm, UV Index predicted to reach 4 [Moderate]</text>
            </forecast-period>
            <forecast-period index="1" start-time-local="2026-04-22T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-04-23T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-04-21T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-04-22T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Partly cloudy. Medium chance of showers, most likely in the early morning. Winds north to northwesterly 15 to 25 km/h becoming light before dawn then becoming south to southeasterly 15 to 25 km/h in the morning. Overnight temperatures falling to around 15 with daytime temperatures reaching the low 20s.</text>
